<p>Construction dust from plaster, silica and building materials can remain airborne long after renovation work finishes.</p>
<h2>Why construction dust is harmful</h2>
<p>Fine particles can irritate lungs, eyes and skin, particularly in enclosed residential spaces.</p>
<h2>Proper removal</h2>
<p>Professional after builders cleaning removes these particles using HEPA filtration and controlled surface cleaning.</p>
